<p><strong>SCP-CN-1197：</strong>乐群湖水怪</p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2020年2月1日</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/falconiformes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5842934); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5842934&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569464" alt="Falconiformes" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5842934)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/falconiformes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5842934); return false;">Falconiformes</a></span></p>
<p><strong>插图：</strong>来自百度贴吧，图片原网址：<a href="http://tieba.baidu.com/photo/p?kw=%E7%9C%81%E9%94%A1%E4%B8%AD&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;flux=1&amp;tid=5144982616&amp;pic_id=b7b9cab44aed2e73dddf93448d01a18b86d6fae3&amp;pn=1&amp;fp=2&amp;see_lz=1">http://tieba.baidu.com/photo/p?kw=%E7%9C%81%E9%94%A1%E4%B8%AD&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;flux=1&amp;tid=5144982616&amp;pic_id=b7b9cab44aed2e73dddf93448d01a18b86d6fae3&amp;pn=1&amp;fp=2&amp;see_lz=1</a></p>
